<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10692666>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Inga vera seeds with ovoid galls: Galls with Allorhogas lavraensis and Eurytoma sp. in the upper and middle part of the seed, respectively." ;
